        </a>
                    </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_277969706" data-seq="277969707" data-pid="277969706" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8153606/277969706.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:906px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D4/88/wKgBEFpHpbiAOoAOAA4GaD2CCik74.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D4/88/wKgBEFpHpbiAOoAOAA4GaD2CCik74.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277969706" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="277971689">
            估计是冬天的缘故，游人并不多，安检和买票都没有排队的现象。刚开始想直冲里面去参观，又想想无从开始，正好看到门口有一个团队那里有讲解员在讲解，于是老老实实地跟在一起吧。讲解员高大姐讲解风格比较活跃，非常幽默，让我们了解了一些我们所不知道的和珅的秘密，不管是正史还是野史，就当是真的吧。<br />
恭王府里面还有许多的文物展览，好多的文物是从海关缉私处移交过来的，喜欢历史的朋友值得去参观一下。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_277969713" data-seq="277969714" data-pid="277969713" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8153606/277969713.html">
