        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="277971832">
            恭王府出来，简单地吃了点东西，去酒店办理入住，这样可以把行李放在房间里，下午就轻装上阵了。<br />
下午的第一站是国子监，继续跟着里面的讲解员蹭听，讲真，如果没有讲解，估计半个小时就可以出来了，只是走马观花，完全没有相关的知识可以了解。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_277969775" data-seq="277969776" data-pid="277969775" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8153606/277969775.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D4/91/wKgBEFpHpcaAOhxfAA_4hZMYmP482.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D4/91/wKgBEFpHpcaAOhxfAA_4hZMYmP482.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277969775" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="277971500">
            国子监参观完毕，来到了网上热推的五道营胡同，事实上，经过之前的游览，体力有所下降，于是找了一家甜品店休息了一会儿，就当作下午的收官之作。<br />
晚饭本来纠结于去东来顺还是全聚德，后来还是决定去东来顺，早早地过去，没想到已经有几桌在吃了。手切羊肉明显比冻肉更嫩，值得推荐。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_277969804" data-seq="277969806" data-pid="277969804" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8153606/277969804.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D4/94/wKgBEFpHpcqAK9jyAAmKxActX9g75.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D4/94/wKgBEFpHpcqAK9jyAAmKxActX9g75.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277969804" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_277969851" data-seq="277969852" data-pid="277969851" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8153606/277969851.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D4/97/wKgBEFpHpc6ABr3MAAkas-o6Q6I74.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D4/97/wKgBEFpHpc6ABr3MAAkas-o6Q6I74.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277969851" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="277972092">
            酒足饭饱之后，按计划来到今天的最后一站，奥体中心，鸟巢和水立方在灯光的映射下，特别漂亮，鸟巢里很热闹的样子，应该是有什么活动在里面举行，也没去打听了，我来只是拍照的。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_277947817" data-seq="277969880" data-pid="277947817" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8153606/277947817.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/C9/53/wKgBEFpHlqmAZeVnAAoWx1Bauy806.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/C9/53/wKgBEFpHlqmAZeVnAAoWx1Bauy806.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277947817" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_277969887" data-seq="277969888" data-pid="277969887" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8153606/277969887.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D4/9E/wKgBEFpHpdSAeOd4AAgfd4Ti_f889.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D4/9E/wKgBEFpHpdSAeOd4AAgfd4Ti_f889.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277969887" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="277972303">
            回到酒店，胡乱地写下这些文字，算是交差吧。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_277969910" data-seq="277969911" data-pid="277969910" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8153606/277969910.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:906px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D4/A1/wKgBEFpHpdeACDy3AAb9-FLUQFs94.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D4/A1/wKgBEFpHpdeACDy3AAb9-FLUQFs94.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277969910" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
    
